formThreeBId.notesToCertificate: In Form 3 (Annexure), whereever Date of agreement of sale is not available, we have mentioned date of execution of sale deed.As per Vikas Parvangi there are 144 Units, but as per the last return uploaded only 75 units are recognised. Hence in form 3A, booked and unbooked Inventories are of those 75 units only.While computing withdrawls from the bank account, we have considered total receipts during the period and balance lying in RERA Bank Account as base for computing withdrawable amount on account of construction. The preparation of the accompanying Statement is the responsibility of the Management of the Company. This responsibility includes designing, implementing and maintaining internal control relevant to the preparation and presentation of the Statement, and applying an appropriate basis of preparation; and making estimates that are reasonable in the circumstances. WE HAVE NOT AUDITED BOOKS OF ACCOUNTS AND HAVE PREPARED THE CERTIFICATE BASIS THE DATA PROVIDED TO US Bank details are taken as per books of accounts. In some cases the amount received is more than the unit consideration amount in such cases we have restricted the receipt up to the unit consideration. We do not certify the carpet area, balcony area or wash area the same is taken as provided by the management. KYC detaills of the allottees are taken as provided by the management. in cases where sale deed is executed the date of sale deed is taken.
